t: Seether - Seether: 2002-2013 - Amazon.com Music
s: The second cd is the reason I purchased it. This one contains all of the songs that you can't listen to on the radio or previous releases. The sondtracks, demos and b sides for singles released elsewhere. As always, Morgan's lyrics and voice are perfect. The music itself is a wide range of the hard hitting rock songs that we love from this band as well as a couple ballads thrown in for good measure. Love this collection and I hope for many more from Seether ...
